    #   HCOOH + H2 = CH2O + H2O
    #   CO2 + 4 H2 = CH4 + 2 H2O
    #   2 CO2 + 2 H2 = 2 CH2O + O2
    #   2 CO2 + 4 H2 = 2 CH3OH + O2
    #   2 HCOOH + 2 H2 = 2 CH3OH + O2
    edge [color="#984EA3"]
    "CO" -> "CO + H2 = CH2O"
    "H2" -> "CO + H2 = CH2O"
    "CO + H2 = CH2O" -> "CH2O"
    "CO" -> "CO + H2O = HCOOH"

    "H2" -> "CO2 + H2 = HCOOH"

    "CO2 + H2 = HCOOH" -> "HCOOH"
    "CO" -> "2 CO + O2 = 2 CO2"

    "H2" -> "CH2O + H2 = CH3OH"

    "HCOOH + H2 = CH4 + O2" -> "CH4"
    "H2" -> "CH3OH + H2 = CH4 + H2O"

    "CH3OH + H2 = CH4 + H2O" -> "H2O"
    "H2" -> "CH2O + 2 H2 = CH4 + H2O"
    "CH2O" -> "CH2O + 2 H2 = CH4 + H2O"
    "CH2O + 2 H2 = CH4 + H2O" -> "CH4"
    "CH2O + 2 H2 = CH4 + H2O" -> "H2O"
    "H2" -> "HCOOH + H2 = CH2O + H2O"
    "HCOOH" -> "HCOOH + H2 = CH2O + H2O"
    "HCOOH + H2 = CH2O + H2O" -> "H2O"
    "HCOOH + H2 = CH2O + H2O" -> "CH2O"
    "H2" -> "CO2 + 4 H2 = CH4 + 2 H2O"
    "CO2" -> "CO2 + 4 H2 = CH4 + 2 H2O"
    "CO2 + 4 H2 = CH4 + 2 H2O" -> "CH4"

    "H2" -> "2 CO2 + 2 H2 = 2 CH2O + O2"
    "CO2" -> "2 CO2 + 2 H2 = 2 CH2O + O2"
    "2 CO2 + 2 H2 = 2 CH2O + O2" -> "O2"
    "2 CO2 + 2 H2 = 2 CH2O + O2" -> "CH2O"
    "H2" -> "2 CO2 + 4 H2 = 2 CH3OH + O2"
    "CO2" -> "2 CO2 + 4 H2 = 2 CH3OH + O2"
    "2 CO2 + 4 H2 = 2 CH3OH + O2" -> "O2"
    "2 CO2 + 4 H2 = 2 CH3OH + O2" -> "CH3OH"
    "H2" -> "2 HCOOH + 2 H2 = 2 CH3OH + O2"
    "HCOOH" -> "2 HCOOH + 2 H2 = 2 CH3OH + O2"
    "2 HCOOH + 2 H2 = 2 CH3OH + O2" -> "O2"
    "2 HCOOH + 2 H2 = 2 CH3OH + O2" -> "CH3OH"

    # pathway 1724:
    #   CO + H2O = HCOOH
    #   CO2 + H2 = HCOOH
    #   2 CO + O2 = 2 CO2
    #   CH2O + H2 = CH3OH
    #   CO + 2 H2 = CH3OH

    #   CO + H2O = HCOOH

    #   2 CO + O2 = 2 CO2
